        <p>Also: a British games show is in big trouble</p>

        
    </div>

      <figure>
          <picture>
  <source srcset="https://aftermath.site/content/images/size/w320/format/webp/2026/02/Screenshot-2026-02-27-164147.png 320w, https://aftermath.site/content/images/size/w640/format/webp/2026/02/Screenshot-2026-02-27-164147.png 600w, https://aftermath.site/content/images/size/w960/format/webp/2026/02/Screenshot-2026-02-27-164147.png 960w, https://aftermath.site/content/images/size/w1280/format/webp/2026/02/Screenshot-2026-02-27-164147.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1023px) 90vw, 1200px" type="image/webp">
  
